snippet.title: How To Survive Review - Worth A Buy?
snippet.description:
You're shipwrecked on an isolated island, a desperate castaway in a total freakshow world. How will you survive? - Well it will be very easy because this game is a hand holding pile of bantha piss....sorry I mean...Is It Worth A Buy?
